534
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:24,240
[SPEAKER_00] Poslije nas četnici je vam doći.

535
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,319
[SPEAKER_00] Skupili smo ih ko?

536
00:23:25,319 --> 00:23:26,839
