542
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] mi ćemo ostati.

543
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ostanite, pružili ruku,

544
00:23:33,859 --> 00:23:35,039
