551
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo sam odlučivo o životima nečijima.

552
00:23:46,859 --> 00:23:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu sam uzeti svakog ubit.

553
00:23:48,539 --> 00:23:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nema policije.

554
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,819
