558
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si sud, sudac.

559
00:23:56,599 --> 00:23:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš raditi što god želiš.

560
00:23:58,880 --> 00:23:59,859
