608
00:25:04,059 --> 00:25:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nisim še.

609
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:06,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ranjivim skupinam.

610
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,619
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mi smo opet sad

