[SPEAKER_00] jer mladi mogu sve.

642
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,839
[SPEAKER_00] Samo moraju vjeruat u sebe.

643
00:25:40,839 --> 00:25:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ako smo mi mogli

644
00:25:42,539 --> 00:25:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] zaustaviti onakvu silu

645
00:25:44,559 --> 00:25:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] JNA,

646
00:25:45,980 --> 00:25:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Četnike,

647
00:25:46,779 --> 00:25:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] nema kog nije bilo

648
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] sve na nas išo.

649
00:25:48,819 --> 00:25:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ako smo uspjeli zaustaviti

650
00:25:50,759 --> 00:25:51,859
[SPEAKER_00] i držati ih jedno

651
00:25:51,859 --> 00:25:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] šest mjeseci

652
