664
00:26:05,619 --> 00:26:06,299
[SPEAKER_00] najstariji je imao.

665
00:26:06,299 --> 00:26:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ti si imao 22

666
00:26:07,539 --> 00:26:08,759
[SPEAKER_01] najstarije u Turbovodu

667
00:26:08,759 --> 00:26:09,480
[SPEAKER_01] imao 20 godina.

668
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,200
[SPEAKER_00] 25, da.

669
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:13,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, daj mi, evo sad govoriš

670
00:26:13,319 --> 00:26:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] o mladima, daj, dozovi nam to

671
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] kakav si ti bio prije tog rata,

672
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:20,200
[SPEAKER_01] kako si živio, šta si želio,

673
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, i u što te to prebazi.

674
00:26:22,180 --> 00:26:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] I kako je to uopće, ta transformacija

675
00:26:24,460 --> 00:26:27,740
[SPEAKER_01] u ratnika, u borca, u nekog

676
00:26:27,740 --> 00:26:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] ko prolazi ovakve nevjerojatne stvari

677
