692
00:26:51,299 --> 00:26:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne, ne, ne, ne, trebamo.

693
00:26:51,819 --> 00:26:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ni danas ne znaju mnogi

694
