700
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] To se onda moglo,

701
00:27:02,779 --> 00:27:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] to se zvalo dodatna,

702
00:27:03,819 --> 00:27:06,920
