715
00:27:22,500 --> 00:27:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Živi na Borovju.

716
00:27:24,619 --> 00:27:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] Sto poslati invalid.

717
00:27:26,839 --> 00:27:28,660
