720
00:27:38,099 --> 00:27:39,279
[SPEAKER_00] iza nastadena detonacija.

721
00:27:39,279 --> 00:27:40,319
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio skrikinio šljem

722
00:27:40,319 --> 00:27:42,240
[SPEAKER_00] minut prije i na srado.

723
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,700
[SPEAKER_00] Sto poslati invalid.

724
00:27:43,700 --> 00:27:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, a mogli smo to sve,

725
00:27:45,099 --> 00:27:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] Filipa uzeti, otići u Zagreb,

726
00:27:46,299 --> 00:27:46,859
