[SPEAKER_00] i da me se uopće...

730
00:27:49,980 --> 00:27:51,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ste odabrali ostati.

731
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] Odabrali smo ostati

732
00:27:52,259 --> 00:27:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] za dobrobit ljudi

733
