[SPEAKER_01] ali i dalje ne razumijete.

739
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne razumijem.

740
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu ja to razumijet.

741
00:28:02,859 --> 00:28:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] I nikad neću razumijet.

742
