[SPEAKER_01] Svakoga se to tiče.

1170
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:13,420
[SPEAKER_00] Svakog.

1171
00:37:13,420 --> 00:37:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] To tiče njegovog djeteta.

1172
00:37:14,380 --> 00:37:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] On će raditi za te i plaćat će to.

1173
00:37:16,579 --> 00:37:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mislim, ali taj paradoks toga

1174
00:37:18,739 --> 00:37:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] da se danas, 2021. ide financirati

1175
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:25,219
[SPEAKER_01] one koji su stvorili ratne štete

1176
00:37:25,219 --> 00:37:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] za koje Hrvatska nije dobila novac,

1177
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,860
[SPEAKER_01] nikakvo obištećenje.

1178
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:30,519
[SPEAKER_01] Da se sada njih na kraju obištećaju,

1179
00:37:30,519 --> 00:37:32,599
[SPEAKER_01] to je doista nema tu...

1180
00:37:32,599 --> 00:37:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] A ne bi palo Andreju Plenkoviću,

1181
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] napravim, takvom velikom diplomati,

1182
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] da traži ratnu štete u Srbiju za nas zlogore,

1183
00:37:37,619 --> 00:37:40,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji smo prošli na desetke tisuća Hrvate,

1184
00:37:40,239 --> 00:37:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] prošlo pa kao logora.

1185
00:37:41,179 --> 00:37:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] I u Srbiji, u Logorima, tako i u Hrvatskoj,

1186
00:37:45,519 --> 00:37:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] i u Crnoj gori, i u Bosni i Hercegovini

1187
00:37:48,059 --> 00:37:50,780
[SPEAKER_00] su odvodili naše ljude na početku ratu

1188
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] da kaže, a morate plato što to,

1189
00:37:53,139 --> 00:37:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] bili ste strana u ratu,

1190
00:37:54,219 --> 00:37:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] ako niste bili u stranu u ratu,

1191
00:37:55,860 --> 00:37:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa što je Mlinarić i tisuće druge

1192
00:37:57,679 --> 00:37:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] radilo u Nišu, u Zatvoru,

1193
00:37:59,099 --> 00:38:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] u Stajićevo i u Sremskoj Mitrovici.

1194
00:38:00,539 --> 00:38:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju krajeva postoji dokumenti

1195
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] Međunanog Crvenog križa

1196
00:38:03,159 --> 00:38:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji su nas popisali,

1197
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:05,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači jedan kroz jedan.

1198
00:38:05,179 --> 00:38:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ako niste bili strana u ratu,

1199
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] rekli ste, oni su to sve vadili,

1200
00:38:09,239 --> 00:38:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] ili ja sam osjetio na svojoj kože

1201
00:38:11,059 --> 00:38:13,019
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo ja i ti ljudi koji su bili po Logorima,

1202
00:38:13,019 --> 00:38:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] što znači do priznanja Hrvatske

1203
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] i poslije priznanja.

1204
00:38:16,079 --> 00:38:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] Do priznanja Hrvatske smo uvijekat

1205
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] pobunjenik taj, taj.

1206
00:38:19,739 --> 00:38:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je Hrvatska priznata 15.1.1992,

1207
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] onda je bil tako zarubljenik.

1208
00:38:23,019 --> 00:38:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači mi smo po njima bili tada pobunjenici,

1209
00:38:26,099 --> 00:38:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako smo poslije 15.1.

1210
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:28,840
[SPEAKER_00] kada je Hrvatska priznata

1211
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] što nisu otvorili vrata,

1212
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] rekli, idite, pustili vas tako doma.

1213
00:38:32,079 --> 00:38:33,139
[SPEAKER_00] Znači nisu to napravili.

1214
00:38:33,139 --> 00:38:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] Niko ne pita za naše oštete,

1215
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] a to su najugroženija skupina

1216
00:38:37,119 --> 00:38:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] branitelja, su Logoraši.

1217
00:38:39,039 --> 00:38:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] U prošijek u miru sa 53 godine.

1218
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] To sam sigurno.

1219
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, s obzirom na muke koje ste preživili.

1220
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] I na stres i na sve.

1221
00:38:45,079 --> 00:38:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] I na sve što ste pretrpjeli.

1222
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nekako, kako ti,

1223
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] ja uvijek me jako zasmeta

1224
00:38:53,679 --> 00:38:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] kad čujem da netko kaže

1225
00:38:54,679 --> 00:38:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] kakva je ovo država.

1226
00:38:55,699 --> 00:38:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je divna država.

1227
00:38:58,420 --> 00:39:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] To isto kao da bi čovjek rekao

1228
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] za svoje djete kako je.

1229
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:04,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, država je fenomenalna.

1230
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je stvorio za nas Hrvata,

1231
00:39:06,239 --> 00:39:08,219
[SPEAKER_00] ali vlast treba mijenjati.

1232
00:39:08,219 --> 00:39:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] Točka, amen, nema gotovo.

1233
00:39:09,920 --> 00:39:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] Država uvijek se mora voliti.

1234
00:39:12,139 --> 00:39:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] Država je prekrasna

1235
00:39:13,559 --> 00:39:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] od Slavonje ravne,

1236
00:39:15,099 --> 00:39:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] od Brežuljaka,

1237
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] Zagorskih,

1238
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,179
[SPEAKER_00] od like,

1239
00:39:18,179 --> 00:39:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] brdovite,

1240
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] planinske,

1241
00:39:20,519 --> 00:39:22,300
[SPEAKER_00] do mora našeg Jadranskog prekrasnog.

1242
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] Nema ljepše države na svijetu za živjeti.

1243
00:39:24,139 --> 00:39:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] Razina frustracije te

1244
00:39:29,059 --> 00:39:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] među ljudima koji su ovakve žrtve podnijeli

1245
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,340
[SPEAKER_01] kao ti i kao mnogi drugi.

1246
00:39:33,340 --> 00:39:36,579
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je uvijek kad su ovakve nekakve situacije

1247
00:39:36,579 --> 00:39:38,420
[SPEAKER_01] kada se vrijeđa branitelje,

1248
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:40,159
[SPEAKER_01] kad se omalovažava domovinski rat,

1249
00:39:40,159 --> 00:39:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] kad se laže ljudima u lice,

1250
00:39:41,659 --> 00:39:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] ja se uvijek pitam kako je to onima

1251
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] koji su najveće žrtve dali.

1252
00:39:45,719 --> 00:39:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] brata si ti svog dao,

1253
00:39:47,199 --> 00:39:47,780
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1254
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:49,840
[SPEAKER_01] moja tri brata su živa.

1255
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] Hoću reći,

1256
00:39:51,539 --> 00:39:53,739
[SPEAKER_01] koliko je to teško

1257
00:39:53,739 --> 00:39:55,219
[SPEAKER_01] izdržavati ljudima,

1258
00:39:55,219 --> 00:39:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] samo ono što slušaju

1259
00:39:57,039 --> 00:40:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] i što mediji kreiraju neistine,

1260
00:40:00,079 --> 00:40:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] jedan dio medija.

1261
00:40:01,039 --> 00:40:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, Željka, ja opraštam svima sve.

1262
00:40:03,139 --> 00:40:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] I neprijateljima koji su me tukli,

1263
00:40:05,260 --> 00:40:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja opraštam sve,

1264
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno sve.

1265
00:40:07,599 --> 00:40:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ne opraštam jedino

1266
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] političarima našima.

1267
00:40:11,260 --> 00:40:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam očekivao

1268
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] od Šlivančina da će donet meni bombone,

1269
00:40:14,719 --> 00:40:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ne razumijem.

1270
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam od njega očekivao

1271
00:40:16,699 --> 00:40:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je bilo.

1272
00:40:17,239 --> 00:40:18,559
[SPEAKER_01] Pa niti od Stanimirovića

1273
00:40:18,559 --> 00:40:19,219
[SPEAKER_01] nisi očekivao

1274
00:40:19,219 --> 00:40:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] da se bori za Hrvatsku.

1275
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] Niti od Stanimirovića,

1276
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] niti očekavim od Pupu

1277
00:40:21,900 --> 00:40:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] da se bori za ovo.

1278
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ali bom je od Plenkovića

1279
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] očekujem.

1280
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:26,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne očekujem

1281
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] niti od Plenkovića

1282
00:40:28,159 --> 00:40:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] da se bori više za mene.

1283
00:40:29,559 --> 00:40:31,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ni da se bori

1284
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] za oštetu,

1285
00:40:32,780 --> 00:40:33,139
[SPEAKER_00] logu,

1286
00:40:33,139 --> 00:40:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] da mene novac.

1287
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, sad javno kažem,

1288
00:40:35,099 --> 00:40:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] a rekao sam to još

1289
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] u jednoj emisiji.

1290
00:40:37,059 --> 00:40:37,860
[SPEAKER_00] javno kažem,

1291
00:40:37,860 --> 00:40:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] to je krvav novac.

1292
00:40:39,079 --> 00:40:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Krvavo sam ga batin

1293
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ga zaradilo

1294
00:40:41,079 --> 00:40:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] to što bi Srblja

1295
00:40:41,780 --> 00:40:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] trebala isplatiti.

1296
00:40:42,599 --> 00:40:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga poklanjam

1297
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] bolestnoj djeci.

1298
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Prekrvavo sam ga zaradio

1299
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ga pre lagano potrošio.

1300
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja ga moram dat negdje

1301
00:40:50,219 --> 00:40:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] gdje znam da će...

1302
00:40:51,179 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako teško.

1303
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je teško.

1304
00:40:52,659 --> 00:40:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mene to ne zanima novac.

1305
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mene zanima presuda za povijest.

1306
00:40:57,539 --> 00:40:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nabijat će nam ove ustaše

1307
00:40:59,260 --> 00:41:00,360
[SPEAKER_00] koje meni nabije

1308
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] koje sam ođa 69. godine

1309
00:41:01,599 --> 00:41:02,480
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu se oprati

1310
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] od toga nazivati.

1311
00:41:03,139 --> 00:41:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, i dalje će o tome pričat,

1312
00:41:05,300 --> 00:41:05,760
[SPEAKER_01] lagat.

1313
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da je u Hrvatskoj

1314
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] postoji srpska propagandna mašina.

1315
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] Jasno, jasno.

1316
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:11,719
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, i zamjeram politici

1317
00:41:11,719 --> 00:41:13,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači, krajem, opraštam sve.

1318
00:41:13,179 --> 00:41:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] Rat, logor, ništa me to

1319
00:41:15,079 --> 00:41:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno sve oprašta.

1320
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne opraštam im politici

1321
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] našoj odnos prema mladima

1322
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] da naši mladi moraju bježati

1323
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] iz ove pravljajpe države.

1324
00:41:22,199 --> 00:41:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] To im ne moglo prosto nikako.

1325
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] Zato sam se uključio

1326
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] u ovu političku borbu

1327
00:41:25,659 --> 00:41:26,820
[SPEAKER_00] i zato ću se boriti

1328
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] isto koji se borio u Vukovara.

1329
00:41:28,239 --> 00:41:30,159
[SPEAKER_00] Bez kompromisa u kost,

1330
00:41:30,159 --> 00:41:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] u glavu, stalno

1331
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] i bez kompromisa.

1332
00:41:33,159 --> 00:41:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] I koje sad su koraci

1333
00:41:35,400 --> 00:41:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] vezane za ovaj zakon

1334
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:37,440
[SPEAKER_01] o civilnim želitvama rata?

1335
00:41:37,539 --> 00:41:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] Što je ono što se sad tu može napraviti

1336
00:41:39,659 --> 00:41:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] da se spriječi Plenkovića

1337
00:41:41,539 --> 00:41:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] da provede zakon

1338
00:41:42,539 --> 00:41:43,139
[SPEAKER_01] koji je štetan

1339
00:41:43,139 --> 00:41:44,699
[SPEAKER_01] na štetu Hrvatske?

1340
00:41:44,699 --> 00:41:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možete vi tu napraviti ništa

1341
00:41:46,639 --> 00:41:47,679
[SPEAKER_00] kao oporba.

1342
00:41:47,679 --> 00:41:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam siguran

1343
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] i u generala Sačića

1344
00:41:50,139 --> 00:41:52,119
[SPEAKER_00] da će staviti amanumane.

1345
00:41:52,119 --> 00:41:53,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću staviti amanumane na zakon.

1346
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mirobulj, očitavno os će staviti.

1347
00:41:55,500 --> 00:41:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Mirobulj, obaveza će staviti.

1348
00:41:56,420 --> 00:41:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] Mirobulj, obaveza će staviti.

1349
00:41:57,340 --> 00:41:58,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nos spomenuo mi ja bulja svoga.

1350
00:41:58,059 --> 00:41:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga nevam.

1351
00:41:59,039 --> 00:42:00,699
[SPEAKER_00] Mi tamo koj jedan

1352
00:42:00,699 --> 00:42:01,760
[SPEAKER_00] kad nastupamo.

1353
00:42:02,239 --> 00:42:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ja uopće ne samim

1354
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] u nastrojicu

1355
00:42:05,059 --> 00:42:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] da ćemo pokušati

1356
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] da dopravamo sam

1357
00:42:06,739 --> 00:42:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali nažalost

1358
00:42:07,619 --> 00:42:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] oni imaju većinu

1359
00:42:09,119 --> 00:42:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ali ima u HDZ-u

1360
00:42:10,519 --> 00:42:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] branitelja ljudi

1361
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:13,119
[SPEAKER_01] koji su sisto s vama boreli

1362
00:42:13,119 --> 00:42:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa treba i njih potaknuti

1363
00:42:14,719 --> 00:42:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] da se i oni

1364
00:42:15,300 --> 00:42:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] Sagnu glavu, rekao sam te.

1365
00:42:17,059 --> 00:42:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] Sagnu glavu stedi.

1366
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:17,880
[SPEAKER_01] Možda neće.

1367
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram lići.

1368
00:42:18,719 --> 00:42:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se uvijek nadam

1369
00:42:20,199 --> 00:42:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] da će ljudi...

1370
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš što će reći mi?

